<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gastronomy & Architecture - Malta</title>
    <style>
        /* ==========================================
           Configurações Gerais (Mantendo o Padrão)
           ========================================== */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Georgia, serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #fcf8f2; /* Creme suave */
            color: #4a3f35; /* Marrom escuro */
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Botão Voltar Fixo e Discreto */
        .back-btn {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            background-color: #f4ece1;
            border: 1px solid #e6dac8;
            color: #4a3f35;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            z-index: 10;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background-color: #ebe0cf;
            transform: translateX(-3px);
        }

        /* Cabeçalho */
        .header-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px 40px 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #8c7864;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .header-section p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #706356;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Container Principal */
        .main-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* ==========================================
           Blocos de Conteúdo (Layout de Destaque)
           ========================================== */
        .showcase-block {
            background-color: #f4ece1; /* Bege calcário */
            border: 1px solid #e6dac8;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(140, 120, 100, 0.05);
        }

        .showcase-block h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: #735e49;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e6dac8;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .location-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dfcfbe;
            color: #5c4f43;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .block-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #4a3f35;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* Galeria de Imagens Internas */
        .image-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .image-card {
            background: #fcf8f2;
            border: 1px solid #e6dac8;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .image-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .image-card:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }

        .image-caption {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #706356;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f4ece1;
            border-top: 1px solid #e6dac8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Link de retorno para a Home principal -->
    <a href="index.html" class="back-btn">← Back to Home</a>

    <header class="header-section">
        <h1>Flavors & Stones</h1>
        <p>A journey through Maltese culinary traditions and majestic coastal architecture.</p>
    </header>

    <main class="main-container">

        <!-- Seção 1: Giorgio's Cafeteria -->
        <section class="showcase-block">
            <h2>Giorgio's Cafeteria</h2>
            <div class="location-badge">📍 17, Tigné Seafront, Sliema, Malta</div>
            
            <p class="block-text">
                Established as a beloved landmark on the Sliema waterfront, Giorgio's Cafeteria offers the perfect fusion of Mediterranean vibes and delicious treats. It is the ultimate spot to enjoy a relaxing espresso, authentic local pastries, and savory dishes while taking in stunning open views of the Valletta harbor.
            </p>

            <!-- Grid de Fotos da Cafeteria -->
            <div class="image-grid">
                <div class="image-card">
                    <img src="giorgios-outdoor.webp" alt="Giorgio's Cafeteria Outdoor Seating">
                    <div class="image-caption">The vibrant outdoor terrace facing the Mediterranean Sea</div>
                </div>
                <div class="image-card">
                    <img src="giorgios-food.webp" alt="Traditional Maltese food at Giorgio's">
                    <div class="image-caption">Authentic local flavors and freshly baked desserts</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Seção 2: Mediterranean Architecture -->
        <section class="showcase-block">
            <h2>Iconic Coastal Architecture</h2>
            <div class="location-badge">🏛️ Sliema District</div>
            
            <p class="block-text">
                Malta's landscape is famous for its glowing globigerina limestone buildings. Right around the corner from the lively cafes, historic monuments stand tall against the blue skies, representing centuries of cultural heritage carved in golden stone.
            </p>

            <!-- Foto de Arquitetura com o nome sugerido da Igreja -->
            <div class="image-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
                <div class="image-card" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
                    <img src="malta06.jpg" alt="Our Lady of Mount Carmel Church">
                    <div class="image-caption"><strong>Our Lady of Mount Carmel Church</strong> – A majestic limestone masterpiece by the bay</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

</body>
</html>
